OL,3,CKeir Starmer vows to close loophole
OL,4,Cthat allowed Gaza family to settle in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,8,Fvowed to close a "loophole" that
OL,9,Fgranted a Palestinian family the right
OL,10,Fto remain in the UK after they applied
OL,11,Funder a scheme designed for Ukrainian
OL,12,Frefugees.
OL,14,FA family of six, displaced from Gaza
OL,15,Fafter their home was destroyed by an
OL,16,Fairstrike during the Israel-Hamas war,
OL,17,Fwas granted the right to stay in the
OL,18,FUK after successfully appealing a
OL,19,Fdecision to refuse their entry under
OL,20,Fthe Ukraine Family Scheme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
