OL,3,CKeir Starmer vows to close loophole
OL,4,Cthat allowed Gaza family to settle in
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FStarmer said the appeal decision was
OL,8,F"wrong," stating that Parliament
OL,9,Fshould set immigration rules and Home
OL,10,FSecretary Yvette Cooper has already
OL,11,Fgot her team "working on closing this
OL,12,Floophole".
OL,14,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,15,Fraised the case at Prime Minister's
OL,16,FQuestions on Wednesday, urging Starmer
OL,17,Fto appeal the decision and introduce
OL,18,Flegislation to clarify the "right to a
OL,19,Ffamily life" under Article 8 of the
OL,20,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights
OL,21,F(ECHR).
