OL,7,FHow did the Palestinian family gain
OL,8,Fthe right to stay?
OL,10,FA mother, father, and their four
OL,11,Fchildren, aged 18, 17, eight, and
OL,12,Fseven, applied in September to enter
OL,13,Fthe UK under the Ukraine Family Scheme
OL,14,Fto join the father's brother, a
OL,15,FBritish citizen who has lived in the
OL,16,FUK since 2007.
OL,18,FTheir application was refused on May
OL,19,F2024 after the Home Office concluded
OL,20,Fthe requirements of the scheme had not
OL,21,Fbeen met.
