OL,7,FThe Ukraine Family Scheme, launched in
OL,8,F2022 after the start of the Ukrainian-
OL,9,FRussian war, was designed to allow
OL,10,Feligible Ukrainian nationals to join
OL,11,Ffamily members or extend their stay in
OL,12,Fthe UK.
OL,14,FMore than 200,000 Ukrainians have
OL,15,Fsince found refuge in the UK.
OL,17,FThe family, who have been granted
OL,18,Fanonymity, had their first appeal
OL,19,Fagainst the Home Office's decision
OL,20,Fdismissed by a first-tier immigration
OL,21,Ftribunal judge in September 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
