OL,7,FHowever, a second appeal was upheld by
OL,8,Fupper tribunal judges in January,
OL,9,Fciting Article 8 of the ECHR.
OL,11,FJudge Hugo Norton-Taylor said in his
OL,12,Fjudgment: "We conclude that the
OL,13,Frespondent's (Home Office's) refusal
OL,14,Fof the collective human rights claim
OL,15,Fdoes not, on the particular facts of
OL,16,Fthese cases, strike a fair balance
OL,17,Fbetween the appellants' interests and
OL,18,Fthose of the public.
