OL,7,F"On a cumulative basis, the weight we
OL,8,Fattach to the considerations weighing
OL,9,Fon the appellants' side of the scales
OL,10,Fdemonstrates a very strong claim
OL,11,Findeed. Put another way, there are
OL,12,Fvery compelling or exceptional
OL,13,Fcircumstances.
OL,15,F"Accordingly, the appellants' appeals
OL,16,Fare allowed."
