OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FSpeaking at PMQs, Badenoch said: "This
OL,8,Fis not what the scheme was designed to
OL,9,Fdo. This decision is completely wrong.
OL,10,FIt cannot be allowed to stand. Is the
OL,11,FGovernment planning to appeal on any
OL,12,Fpoints of law, and if so, which ones?
OL,14,FStarmer replied: "I do not agree with
OL,15,Fthe decision. She's right, it's the
OL,16,Fwrong decision. She hasn't quite done
OL,17,Fher homework, because the decision in
OL,18,Fquestion was taken under the last
OL,19,Fgovernment according to the legal
OL,20,Fframework for the last government.
OL,26,@vD@ROU
