OL,5,CUK
OL,7,F"But let me be clear, it should be
OL,8,FParliament that makes the rules on
OL,9,Fimmigration. It should be the
OL,10,FGovernment that makes the policy, that
OL,11,Fis the principle, and the Home
OL,12,FSecretary is already looking at the
OL,13,Flegal loophole which we need to close
OL,14,Fin this particular case."
OL,16,FBadenoch then urged Starmer to
OL,17,Fintroduce new legislation or amend
OL,18,Fexisting proposals in the Commons,
OL,19,Fwith the Prime Minister responding
OL,20,Fthat work on this is already underway.
